document_data.name: O'Malley
document_data.mainbody: '''O'Malley''' was a small town located on the island of [[Gwynneth]] within the [[Moonshae Isles]].{{Cite interactive atlas}}{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: The Moonshae Isles}}
document_data.Geography: O'Malley was located in the kingdom of [[Corwell]] in southern Gwynneth. The town was located along the halfway point on [[Corwell Road]] between [[Caer Corwell]] in the west and [[Kingsbay (town)|Kingsbay]] in the east. O'Malley sat among the foothills where [[the Highlands]] and [[Cambro Mountains]] met in the shadow of the hidden kingdom of [[Synnoria]].
document_data.Rumors & Legends: Natives of O'Malley had been known to celebrate victories over [[firbolg]] raiders by placing their heads upon spikes and dancing around them.
